{"tid":582802,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"[TG] 每日只討論一個Topic","createTime":"2018-03-06T12:58:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-06T12:58:24.000Z","uid":152322,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"da8111a185a828392cba51bd0e077f1f778d6396","tid":582802,"uid":152322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T12:58:24.000Z","msg":"小弟想開個Telegram Group<br />\n每日既討論內容只會圍繞一個主題<br />\n希望大家可以響充裕既時間下舒適地思考同討論<br />\n從而獲得一個不流於淺既對談及相交既經歷<br />\n<br />\n大約半年前玩過一輪 但由於當時既朋友仔比較被動 變左主要由小弟開topic 局限左主題類型既多元性 所以今次希望朋友仔入group既時候可以帶埋一個你想討論既話題入黎<br />\n三十人為限 會用大家提供既題目玩一輪 再一齊做個review <br />\n感謝支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSc6GM68gvt6qVClGppPSSPV6uB6D-I5qMlHUBHoLOpDiLVlkw/viewform?usp=sf_link\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSc6GM68gvt6qVClGppPSSPV6uB6D-I5qMlHUBHoLOpDiLVlkw%2Fviewform%3Fusp%3Dsf_link&d=FkRYAJ%2BVlyd61e66YX%2B9U0bWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=3d248872\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSc6GM68gvt6qVClGppPSSPV6uB6D-I5qMlHUBHoLOpDiLVlkw/viewform?usp=sf_link</a>"}]}